snippet: The Murfreesboro woman was charged with attempted murder after the police said she tried to abort her 24-week-old fetus.
abstract: Murfreesboro, Tenn, police say Anna Yocca is charged with attempted murder after she reportedly tried to abort 24-week-old fetus with coat hanger.
